
---
## 📄 FILE 3: `.gitignore` (Final Version)
Ensure this is in your root:

```gitignore
# Python
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
develop-eggs/
dist/
downloads/
eggs/
.eggs/
lib/
lib64/
parts/
sdist/
var/
wheels/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
ENV/
env/

# IDEs
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Secrets & credentials
.env
*.key
*.pem
config.json

# Artifacts & data
model/predictor_v*/
mlruns/
data/processed/*.parquet
data/processed/*.csv
!data/processed/.gitkeep
reports/*.html
!reports/.gitkeep

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Logs
*.log

# Testing
.pytest_cache/
.coverage
htmlcov/

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/